.. default-domain:: chpl

.. module:: basicEditions.doc

basicEditions.doc
=================
**Usage**

.. code-block:: chapel

   use basicEditions.doc;


or

.. code-block:: chapel

   import basicEditions.doc;

.. function:: proc myFunc()

   .. note::

      myFunc was removed after the 2.0 edition. It is not available in editions after the 2.0 edition.

   
   This is some function

.. function:: proc myFunc()

   .. note::

      myFunc was added in the Maybe 3.0 edition and is also available in all editions after the Maybe 3.0 edition.

   
   This is some function

.. function:: proc myFunc()

   .. note::

      myFunc is available in the preview edition and is expected to be available in the next new edition.

   
   This is some function

.. function:: proc other()

   .. note::

      other was added in the 2.0 edition and was removed after the Maybe 3.0 edition. It is only available in editions between the 2.0 and Maybe 3.0 editions.

   
   This is some other function

